PHP-WOL application's dependencies :

cron
ping
ethtool, ifconfig (for setup script)
libssh2-php
php5-ldap

Commands to run at the server's install :
	


Warning : ttl = 3 for pings (option "-t 3") !
Can be not enough on big networks with many routers !
(TODO : add parameter for that)

chmod 711 /usr/sbin/sendmail => to send mails with php

chmod 666 => config files
